"<h1>Gargoyle: Help</h1>\n"
"\n"
"<p>Only lower case English letters are supported as input in this version which is enough to play majority of games.</p>\n"
"<p>Games are saved and restored, using the usual commands, in .home/user/.gargoyle folder in the internal storage of the device. Only one *.sav file per game is kept.</p>\n"
"<p>Please note that keys \"MENU\" and \"Play/Stop\" will leave Gargoyle running in the background, however you won't be able to switch back to it! You're highly advised to use the standard way of quitting the games of this genre.</p>\n"
"<h2>Controls</h2>\n"
"<p>Press keys 1-9 quickly several times to get to the required letter using the reference below</p>\n"
"<p><b>0</b> - show this help screen</p>\n"
"<p><b>1</b> - [space].,10</p>\n"
"<p><b>2</b> - abc2</p>\n"
"<p><b>3</b> - def3</p>\n"
"<p><b>4</b> - ghi4</p>\n"
"<p><b>5</b> - jkl5</p>\n"
"<p><b>6</b> - mno6</p>\n"
"<p><b>7</b> - pqrs7</p>\n"
"<p><b>8</b> - tuv8</p>\n"
"<p><b>9</b> - wxyz9</p>\n"
"<p><b>C</b> - delete previous character</p>\n"
"<p><b>OK</b> - enter the current command</p>\n"
"<p><b>MENU</b> - back to Main Menu. Note that Gargoyle will continue running, but you won't be able to switch back to it!</p>\n"
"<p><b>Rotate</b> - change screen orientation (portrate/landscape)</p>\n"
"<p><b>Play/Stop</b> - switch to the default audio player. Note that Gargoyle will continue running, but you won't be able to switch back to it!</p>\n"
"<p><b>Up/Down</b> - previous/next command</p>\n"
"<p><b>Left/Right</b> - move cursor left/right</p>\n"
"<p><b>Wheel Up/Down</b> - page up/down</p>\n"

